moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你呀? 香港落完雨又濕又焗</blockquote><br />\n落完雨涼左，本身都涼，今日落雨有風陰天冇太陽就涼意甚濃，吹埋北風"},{"pid":"7aeee4a045e3d4b288160aa5d1dc0b35ac16bccd","tid":206054,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"今晚乾凍，所以唔太凍，但涼到死"},{"pid":"3543b69fc80067c22c81ba6caca3dc48fc69a91d","tid":206054,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"今朝濕熱 辛苦到"},{"pid":"7bdfeaefcd42b3c3ba21442699231597f7cb1d7b","tid":206054,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"761a5fd2f69bc386d68f3a64e4a8bdbd1934ae05","tid":206054,"uid":60487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港果種係濕凍，係全世界最凍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港果種係濕鳩，係全世界最鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港果種係濕滯，係全世界最滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855f3e62b43241efaed7479a98fce03303155665","tid":206054,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"乾熱唔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你試下澳洲既夏天。同樣度數（e.g. 36度）我覺得威力勁過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aefc32a86dfb9353bcf1856d51000c59d5d235","tid":206054,"uid":100716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"又濕又熱好辛喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一出街個頭同身就笠哂"},{"pid":"f4545876111c4d968516e7f39c44f39131938687","tid":206054,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乾熱唔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你試下澳洲既夏天。同樣度數（e.g. 36度）我覺得威力勁過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港 個頭濕哂"},{"pid":"0ba2dd6eebe44f11672942